      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about like, getting drunk or anything. just the single glass of wine i always have. i feel like it shouldn't be a huge deal if it's just a tiny bit of alcohol. won't the alcohol just help the pill kick in a little quicker so i dont lay there tossing and turning for hours?",
