    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just trying to figure out if i'm being paranoid here. if i only have like 4 or 5 oz of wine, is it really going to make a difference in terms of my breathing or something? it doesn't seem like a tiny bit of wine would be life threatening, it just feels like it would help the zolpidem do its job more efficiently.",
